name: Chiptune University - Little Brother (Green)
description:
Our original design in Leaf Green.

All products are currently PRE-ORDER with the stock to be received on the 18th of November. All sales will be held until this time, and will be limited in numbers. 

The stock will be based on a first come first served basis, until the item is marked as 'sold out' 

With each purchase you will receive an added extra; could be a Chiptune album, gift certificate, stickers or even a free tee!

Sizes are based on 'standard' i.e. Fruit of the Loom sizes.

Enjoy!
